title: RNA Seq Analysis
text:
Having some experience of analyzing gene expression data with various tools from GeneSpring through edgeR and more recently having followed tutorials on Single-cell RNA-seq data analysis using Chipster (Seurat based workflows including SingleR, CellDex, CCA, RPCA [Chipster Tutorials, 2023]), my objective is to go deeper into Seurat to refine understanding using publicly available data-sets.
Some examples of non-proprietary analysis. Work in progress
